   try{

		    newrelic.setCustomAttribute('pageGroup', 'Home');
				newrelic.setPageViewName('/TopCategoriesDisplayView', window.location.hostname);

		     	    if(typeof cookieValue != 'undefined' && cookieValue){
			     	   	newrelic.setCustomAttribute('pageFACC', cookieValue[0]); 
			    		newrelic.setCustomAttribute('pageFACA', cookieValue[1]); 	
		    		}		
				}
			}
			catch (err) {
					console.log(err);

function getCookie(cname) {
try{
    var name = cname+"=";
    var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
    for(var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
            c = c.substring(1);
        }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
             return c.substring(name.length, c.length);            
        }
    }
    return "";
    }
	 catch (err) {
		console.log(err);
	}
}

       <script type="903c91e139f632664713c57e-text/javascript">
        dojo.addOnLoad(function() { 
		shoppingActionsJS.setCommonParameters('-1','10151','10051','G','$');
		shoppingActionsServicesDeclarationJS.setCommonParameters('-1','10151','10051');
	});
	//Declare refresh controller which are used in pagination controls of SearchBasedNavigationDisplay -- both products and articles+videos	
	wc.render.declareRefreshController({
		id: "prodRecommendationRefresh_controller_Petco_Homepage_TopSellers_Guest_ESpot",
		renderContext: wc.render.getContextById("searchBasedNavigation_context"),
		url: "",
		formId: ""
	
		,renderContextChangedHandler: function(message, widget) {
			var controller = this;
			var renderContext = this.renderContext;
			var resultType = renderContext.properties["resultType"];
			if(resultType == "products" || resultType == "both"){
				widget.refresh(renderContext.properties);
				console.log("espot refreshing");
			}
		}
			
		/**
		 * Clears the progress bar after a successful refresh.
		 *
		 * @param {Object} widget The refresh area widget.
		 */
		,postRefreshHandler: function(widget) {
			var controller = this;
			var renderContext = this.renderContext;
			cursor_clear();
			
			var refreshUrl = controller.url;
			var emsName = "";
			var indexOfEMSName = refreshUrl.indexOf("emsName=", 0);
			if(indexOfEMSName >= 0){
				emsName = refreshUrl.substring(indexOfEMSName+8);
				if (emsName.indexOf("&") >= 0) {
					emsName = emsName.substring(0, emsName.indexOf("&"));
					emsName = "script_" + emsName;
				}
			}
				
			if (emsName != "") {
				if (dojo.byId(emsName) != null) {
					var espot = dojo.query('.genericESpot',dojo.byId(emsName).parentNode)[0];
					if (espot != null) {
						dojo.addClass(espot,'emptyESpot');
					}
				}
			}
			dojo.publish("CMPageRefreshEvent");
		}
	});
       </script>

             <script>
              var shopByPetController = (function () {
			var categoryElements = document.getElementsByClassName('pet-category');
			var contentElements = document.getElementsByClassName('shop-by-pet-content');
			var currentCategory = 0;

			function selectCategory(idx) {
				categoryElements[currentCategory].classList.remove('active');
				categoryElements[idx].classList.add('active');
				contentElements[currentCategory].classList.remove('active');
				contentElements[idx].classList.add('active');
				currentCategory = idx;
			}

			return {
				selectCategory: selectCategory
			};
		})();
             </script>

             <li>
              No promo code needed. The promotion and discount will automatically be added to your qualifying subtotal.
             </li>
             <li>
              In order to qualify for the buy online and pickup in-store discount, you must choose the "I'll Pick It Up" option, choose your store and add to your Shopping Cart.
